OL,3,CHiker safe after eight-hour rescue
OL,4,Coperation in Peak District
OL,6,FA hiker is recovering after he was
OL,7,Fsaved by Mountain Rescue teams when he
OL,8,Fbecame stuck in freezing conditions in
OL,9,Fthe Peak District.
OL,11,FSixty members of teams from Glossop,
OL,12,FKinder and Edale battled through ice
OL,13,Fand snow in a dramatic eight-hour
OL,14,Foperation.
OL,16,FMountain rescuers were called out just
OL,17,Fafter 3.20pm on 7 January when the
OL,18,Fwalker got into difficulty in deep
OL,19,Fsnow.
