OL,3,CHiker safe after eight-hour rescue
OL,4,Coperation in Peak District
OL,6,FSo severe were the conditions facing
OL,7,Fthe teams that a Coastguard helicopter
OL,8,Fwas forced to abandon the rescue after
OL,9,Fnumerous attempts to lift the casualty
OL,10,Fout.
OL,12,FThirty members of the Glossop Mountain
OL,13,FRescue Team responded to the incident,
OL,14,Fbefore being joined by 12 from Kinder
OL,15,Fand 18 from Edale, but the volunteers
OL,16,Fwere initially unable to find the man.
OL,18,FOnce he was located, the trekker was
OL,19,Ftreated for hypothermia and
OL,20,Fstretchered back to safety.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
