OL,4,Coperation in Peak District
OL,6,FThe team were finally able to stand
OL,7,Fdown at midnight, with the Glossop
OL,8,Frescuers admitting they "couldn't have
OL,9,Fdone it without the support of our
OL,10,Fneighbouring teams".
OL,12,FA spokesperson for Glossop Mountain
OL,13,FRescue Team added: "The team were
OL,14,Fcalled out 3:21pm to a casualty who
OL,15,Fhad got into difficulty in deep snow.
OL,16,FUnfortunately, we were unable to
OL,17,Fdefine his exact location so the team
OL,18,Fwent out with a number of search
OL,19,Fpatterns across the plateau.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
