OL,3,CHiker safe after eight-hour rescue
OL,4,Coperation in Peak District
OL,6,F"Visibility and mobility across the
OL,7,Fmoor were hampered by snow that was
OL,8,Fdrifting up to 3ft in depth. The
OL,9,Fcasualty was located in the Hern
OL,10,FStones area, assessed and provided
OL,11,Fwith warming blankets due to
OL,12,Fsignificant hypothermia. With the
OL,13,Fpotential for life threatening
OL,14,Finjuries we requested support from the
OL,15,FCoastguard S92 helicopter."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
