OL,3,CHiker safe after eight-hour rescue
OL,4,Coperation in Peak District
OL,6,F"Unfortunately, after several attempts
OL,7,Fthey were forced to turn back by the
OL,8,Fweather on Bleaklow. Considering the
OL,9,Farduous nature of conditions, Kinder
OL,10,Fand Edale mountain rescue teams were
OL,11,Fcalled on to support with the
OL,12,Fstretcher carry back to the roadhead.
OL,14,F"The casualty was transported off the
OL,15,Fhill to snake summit using our new
OL,16,Fsled - fabricated by Wray Engineering
OL,17,F- where he was passed onto the
OL,18,Fawaiting ambulance for further
OL,19,Fassessment and treatment. We wish the
OL,20,Fcasualty a speedy recovery."
